OL,3,CGraduate fostered at 15 says foster
OL,4,Ccarers 'gave her a future'
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports Anna Youssef spoke
OL,7,Fto Codie and her foster parents about
OL,8,Fthe importance of fostering
OL,10,FA graduate who says her foster carers
OL,11,Fgave her a future as well as a home is
OL,12,Fappealing for more people to consider
OL,13,Ffostering.
OL,15,FCodie, 22, was placed into foster
OL,16,Fcare, alongside her two siblings, when
OL,17,Fshe was 15. It was the first and only
OL,18,Fplacement for all of them.
