OL,3,CGraduate fostered at 15 says foster
OL,4,Ccarers 'gave her a future'
OL,6,FShe says her foster carers Lisa and
OL,7,FAlix Schofield-Rowles, from Bolton,
OL,8,Fdid not just give them a place to stay
OL,9,F- they gave them a home and a future.
OL,11,FAfter graduating with a degree in
OL,12,Fpsychology, she has just moved into
OL,13,Fher own flat and is now pursuing a
OL,14,Fcareer in social care.
OL,16,FCodie said: "I'm always coming back. I
OL,17,Fcame back yesterday for my tea. They
OL,18,Fcome and visit me and we still do
OL,19,Fthings together so we are still a
OL,20,Ffamily.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
