OL,3,CGraduate fostered at 15 says foster
OL,4,Ccarers 'gave her a future'
OL,6,F"They've been a massive, massive
OL,7,Fsupport with every little thing, every
OL,8,Fbig thing in my life. I don't think I
OL,9,Fwould be anywhere near where I am now
OL,10,Fif it wasn't for them.
OL,12,FCodie said she was worried the
OL,13,Fsiblings would be split up when they
OL,14,Fentered care, but Alix and her wife
OL,15,FLisa had specifically asked to help a
OL,16,Fsibling group.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
