OL,3,CGraduate fostered at 15 says foster
OL,4,Ccarers 'gave her a future'
OL,6,FAlix said: "I've got brothers myself,
OL,7,FLisa has got a sister. I couldn't
OL,8,Fimagine not being brought up with them
OL,9,Fso I know how important it is for
OL,10,Fsiblings to stay together."
OL,12,FThere is a shortage of 6,500 foster
OL,13,Ffamilies across the country - with the
OL,14,Fnumber of children being placed into
OL,15,Fcare on the rise.
OL,17,F"It's 24/7. It's rewarding," said
OL,18,FLisa, who has now been fostering for
OL,19,Fnearly nine years.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
