OL,3,CGraduate fostered at 15 says foster
OL,4,Ccarers 'gave her a future'
OL,6,F"It has its ups and downs but to see
OL,7,Fchildren come to you who have really
OL,8,Fbig hang ups and leave your home with
OL,9,Fa success story - that's the best
OL,10,Freward you could ever have."
OL,12,FLynda Hardman, director and registered
OL,13,Fmanager at Next Stage for Fostering,
OL,14,Fsaid: "Alix and Lisa prove that
OL,15,Ffostering is more than just providing
OL,16,Fchildren a home ` it is about offering
OL,17,Fsecurity, care and a sense of
OL,18,Fbelonging.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
