OL,3,CGraduate fostered at 15 says foster
OL,4,Ccarers 'gave her a future'
OL,6,F"There is a desperate need for more
OL,7,Ffoster carers, but first, we must
OL,8,Fspread awareness that there is no one-
OL,9,Fsize-fits-all approach to fostering.
OL,11,F"Many people simply do not realise
OL,12,Fthey have the life skills to be an
OL,13,Famazing foster carer and to make a
OL,14,Fdifference to a child's life and
OL,15,Ffuture."
OL,17,FNext Stage for Fostering is actively
OL,18,Fseeking more foster carers across the
OL,19,FNorth West.
